Subject: [PATCH] drm/i915: gen7: implement rczunit workaround
Git-commit: eae66b50c760233fad526edf4a0d327be17a055d
Patch-mainline: 3.3-rc5

This is yet another workaround related to clock gating which we need on
Ivy Bridge.

Bugzilla: https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=41353
Bugzilla: https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=44610
